               <scopecontent id="aspace_05e06ceafb166841486ad74a0787575e">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>One album of photographs documents YMCA scout camps in India (1928) while a second album contains photos of places and people in India and Afghanistan. Twelve albums of negatives as well as loose photographs and negatives, nearly all with identification, document Heinrich's youth, his family, and YMCA work in India and Jerusalem.</p>
